'''Adam Azim''' is the current CEO of the State owned enterprise, Maldives Transport and Contracting Company (MTCC). He was previously the Managing Director of the State Trading Organization (STO).<ref>{{cite web |url=https://mtcc.mv/our-board/adam-azim/ |title=MTCC Board | author= MTCC |date=April 10, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://edition.mv/adam_azim_md_mtcc/25615 |title=MTCC completes 90 projects in 3 years | author= The Edition |date=Aug 28, 2022}}</ref>

