'''Adam Azim''' ({{lang-dv|އާދަމް އާޒިމް}}; born 17 December 1971) is the current [[Mayor]] of [[Malé | Malé City]].<ref>{{Cite news |last= Chaturvedi |first=Amit |date=14 January 2024 |title= Adam Azim: 5 Points On New Mayor Of Male From Pro-India Party |url= https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/adam-azim-5-points-on-new-mayor-of-male-from-pro-india-party-4859569/amp/1 |access-date=14 January 2024 |work=NDTV}}</ref> He was the Chief Executive Officer of the [[State-owned enterprise|state owned enterprise]], Maldives Transport and Contracting Company (MTCC). He was previously the Managing Director of the [[State Trading Organization]] (STO).<ref>{{cite web |author= |date= |title=Adam Azim - MTCC Board |url=https://mtcc.mv/our-board/adam-azim/ |website=MTCC}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |last=Rehan |first=Mohamed |date=28 August 2022 |title=MTCC completes 90 projects in 3 years |url=https://edition.mv/adam_azim_md_mtcc/25615 |work=The Edition}}</ref>
